values.text: Here are the safety protocols you as a passenger need to follow:

As per the guidelines issued by the government, as a passenger, you need to ensure the following things:
1)All passengers traveling are required to use face covers/masks and are required to follow hand hygiene, respiratory hygiene, and environmental hygiene.
2)All passengers are advised to download the 'AAROGYA SETU' app on their mobile phones.
3)Do not travel with symptoms: You are advised to refrain from travel if you show COVID-19 symptoms. In such an event, you might be de-boarded.

We and our travel partners have provided for the following facilities:
1)Hand sanitizer at both doors.
2)Temperature check before entering the bus.
